metadata.name: Date Unknown
metadata.description:
My date is unknown,
I feel it in every bone.

My doubts are there,
but not a tear to share.

Has my time come?
Or will I be safed by some?

Unknown the time is,
Unknown it will stay,
Just like the clock that doesn't say.

My watch is broken,
Like it has never spoken.

A suit is what I wear,
Just to add some flair.

My body I trust,
But it will bring me  to dust.
